 Calderón</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">March 13, 2024</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="article" href="/article/political-violence-mexicos-2024-elections-gender-based-political-violence-against-women"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/GBPVAW%20in%20Mexico%20-%20Infographic.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/GBPVAW%20in%20Mexico%20-%20Infographic.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="GBPVAW in Mexico - Infographic" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Article</div><div class="teaser-topic">Elections</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Political Violence in Mexico&#039;s 2024 Elections: Gender-Based Political Violence Against Women</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">María Calderón</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">March 13, 2024</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="blog-post" href="/blog-post/mexicos-election-will-put-woman-highest-office"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_1670460121.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_1670460121.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="Women March Mexico" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Blog post</div><div class="teaser-topic">Elections</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Mexico’s Election Will Put a Woman 