ender</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">I Belong! How Inclusion Creates a Sense of Belonging and Fuels Genuine Empowerment</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">Julia Taleb</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">March 7, 2024</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="blog-post" href="/blog-post/room-her-own-how-i-created-space-my-empowerment-afghanistan"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2142516189%20%281%29.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2142516189%20%281%29.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="MEP_reading" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Blog post</div><div class="teaser-topic">Women &amp; Gender</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">‘A Room of Her Own’:  How I created a space for my empowerment in Afghanistan</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">Sola Mahfouz</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">March 6, 2024</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="multimedia-50-50" data-layout="right"><div class="multimedia-50-50-inner"><a class="multimedia-50-50-image js-video-modal-open" href="#" data-video="https://youtu.be/BHES7nMJ8hE"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/2up_multimedia/public/media/uploads/images/Screen%20Shot%202020-10-02%20at%209.43.36%20PM.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/2up_mult